#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an4.6:9.1"
msgid "Bahussutaṃ dhammadharaṃ,"
msgstr "A wise disciple of the Buddha"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.6:9.2"
msgid "sappaññaṃ buddhasāvakaṃ;"
msgstr "who has much learning, and has memorized the teachings,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.6:9.3"
msgid "Nekkhaṃ jambonadasseva,"
msgstr "is like a coin of mountain gold."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.6:9.4"
msgid "ko taṃ ninditumarahati;"
msgstr "Who is worthy of criticizing them?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.6:9.5"
msgid "Devāpi naṃ pasaṃsanti,"
msgstr "Even the gods praise them,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.6:9.6"
msgid "brahmunāpi pasaṃsito”ti."
msgstr "and by Brahmā, too, they’re praised.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
